vmenu - dynamic menu
====================
vmenu is an efficient dynamic menu for X.


Requirements
------------
In order to build vmenu you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (vmenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install vmenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running vmenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
